<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=600" />
<title>欢迎注册财说，请激活你的账号</title>
</head>
<body>
<div style="padding-top:40px;font-family:微软雅黑;">
  <div style="padding-left:30px;padding-bottom:30px;border-bottom:1px solid #dfe1e0;margin-bottom:47px;">
    <img src="<%=Setting.html_host%>/images/mail-logo.png" />
  </div>
  <div style="padding-left:66px;width:70%;">
    <div style="color:#000000;font-size:18px;margin-bottom:30px;padding-left:3px;">您离成功注册财说就差一步了 <small>（请在24小时内完成）</small></div>
    <div style="min-width:600px;margin-bottom:40px;width:70%;background:#f4f6f8;padding:40px 30px 15px 40px;">
      <div style="color:#424458;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:20px;">请点击下面的按钮完成注册：</div>
      <a href="<%= new_account_user_url(confirmation_token: @user.confirmation_token) %>" style="color:#FFFFFF;font-size:16px;width:160px;height:44px;background:#64a0d7;text-align:center;line-height:44px;border-radius:3px;cursor:pointer;margin-bottom:34px;display:block;text-decoration:none;">完成注册</a>
      <div style="color:#424458;font-size:14px;">同样您可以点击以下链接完成注册：</div>
      <a href="<%= new_account_user_url(confirmation_token: @user.confirmation_token) %>" style="font-size:14px;color:#0038dc;line-height:28px;text-decoration:none;">
        <%= new_account_user_url(confirmation_token: @user.confirmation_token) %>
      </a>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size:12px;color:#424458;margin-top:76px;margin-bottom:100px;">财说团队</div>
  </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
